claim.claim-text:
A coating, comprising multiple alternating layers of a soft coating and a hard coating comprising:
at least one soft coating;
at least one hard coating; and
a sensor positioned between one soft coating of the at least one soft coating and one hard coating of the at least one hard coating, wherein the sensor comprises a conductive material;
wherein the at least one soft coating and the at least one hard coating have the general formula SiOxCy.
